Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Dialogue
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.16,0:00:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.02,0:00:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.74,0:01:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.99,0:01:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,本想多聊聊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.09,0:01:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,但我害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.65,0:01:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,搞僵氣氛 或者和別人爭吵起來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.13,0:01:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,所以不知不覺 開始不表現自我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.56,0:01:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,希望有人了解我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.86,0:01:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我這個人曾存在過
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.56,0:01:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,只要有人記得
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.80,0:01:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣一來 靈魂就不會死
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.39,0:01:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.40,0:01:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我是高嶋友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.56,0:01:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,奈良縣出身
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.91,0:01:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,生日是1月11日
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.27,0:01:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,血型A 興趣是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.84,0:01:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,空手道
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.31,0:01:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,小時候經常在大自然裡玩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.14,0:01:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,被誤以為是男孩子哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.59,0:01:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,呃 還有還有…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.26,0:01:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,總之就這些
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.54,0:01:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧 若葉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.72,0:01:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 幹吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.83,0:03:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,對方知道牆壁變堅固了 所以著急了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.54,0:03:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,好 一個人打倒三隻就好了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.26,0:03:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,不要大意 上了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.83,0:03:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.05,0:03:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,不用留後手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.92,0:03:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,降臨吧 大天狗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.87,0:03:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,全力全開 來吧 酒吞童子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.26,0:04:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,休想通過這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.37,0:04:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,勇者
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.74,0:04:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,拳
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.39,0:05:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,怪物們 這裡就是你們的葬身之地
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.65,0:05:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,這點程度
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.01,0:05:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,對我四國勇者…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.45,0:06:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,勇者 拳…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.28,0:06:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,湧出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.86,0:06:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,數量好多
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.61,0:07:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼能輸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.52,0:07:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,吃我這招
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.79,0:07:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,勇者踢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.90,0:07:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.48,0:07:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,太巨大了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.78,0:07:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼會 不顧我了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.71,0:07:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.66,0:08:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,誰會讓你去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.39,0:08:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,勇者…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.76,0:08:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,身體 動不了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.29,0:08:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,動起來 動起來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.68,0:08:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,不行 不行…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.05,0:09:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,已經 夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.98,0:09:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,說是要背負什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.11,0:09:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,卻沒能守護
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.65,0:09:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.33,0:09:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,像傻瓜一樣 勇者什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.83,0:09:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,只有疼痛 只有受苦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.47,0:09:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.31,0:09:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,勇者什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.67,0:09:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,勇者什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.77,0:09:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.08,0:09:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,差點被帶走了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.62,0:09:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,動起來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.46,0:09:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,動起來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.45,0:09:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,給我動啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.45,0:10:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,不要被殺手鐧吞噬了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.38,0:10:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,心火滅卻
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.17,0:10:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我們人類很弱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.22,0:10:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,膽小 脆弱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.36,0:10:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,然後 容易落入惡意
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.53,0:10:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.89,0:10:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你說我為什麼戰鬥？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.64,0:10:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,因為是人類！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.95,0:11:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我是高嶋友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.22,0:11:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,大家
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.90,0:11:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,大家
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.10,0:11:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,最喜歡啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.79,0:11:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,千回
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.33,0:11:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,勇者拳
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.47,0:11:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.16,0:12:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.92,0:12:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈 沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.31,0:12:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,若葉 你那邊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.45,0:12:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,結束了 現在不要說話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.80,0:12:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,真不愧是若葉 成功了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.46,0:12:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈 友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.55,0:12:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈 友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.88,0:12:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,不要 不要再有人走了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.04,0:12:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,不要扔下我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.81,0:13:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈死了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.06,0:13:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,千景死了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.36,0:13:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,球子 杏
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.46,0:13:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,大家都死了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.78,0:13:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.05,0:13:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我真是笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.66,0:13:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,明明有人願意為我哭
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.44,0:13:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,希望有人了解我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.61,0:13:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我這個人曾存在過
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.27,0:13:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,只要有人記得
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.97,0:13:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣一來 靈魂就不會死
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.14,0:13:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.10,0:13:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我是乃木若葉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.35,0:13:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,香川縣出身
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.18,0:13:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,生日是6月20日
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.10,0:13:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,血型A
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.22,0:13:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,興趣是鍛鍊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.99,0:13:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,喜歡的食物是烏龍麵
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.26,0:14:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,記住我 了解我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.02,0:14:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我 我們
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.15,0:14:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,是此時此刻 在這個時代戰鬥的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.03,0:14:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,勇者！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.92,0:14:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,然後呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.14,0:14:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,那是那一代的最終戰了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.72,0:14:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,只有若葉活下來了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.81,0:14:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.00,0:14:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,之後為了讓天神平息怒火
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.11,0:14:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,探討實行了奉火祭
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.90,0:14:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,獻上了巫女們
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.68,0:14:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,當代勇者沒有出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.43,0:14:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,記錄就這些
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.26,0:14:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,奉火祭…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.81,0:14:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,就是爭取時間吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.28,0:14:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,整整300年
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.47,0:14:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,要不是園子的先祖大人保護
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.71,0:14:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我們就出生不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.76,0:14:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,守護世界就是指這個？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.40,0:15:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,被託付了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.98,0:15:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,託付給下一代
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.04,0:15:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,還是結束掉 都取決於勇者
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.63,0:15:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,不要說得這麼不吉利
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.61,0:15:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,可是 我們這一代的戰鬥已經…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.16,0:15:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,希望已經結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.99,0:15:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.78,0:15:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,鋤頭？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.11,0:15:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,似乎是很重要的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.71,0:15:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,是鋤頭
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.58,0:15:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,鋤頭
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.65,0:15:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,鋤頭
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.85,0:15:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,鋤頭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.90,0:15:37.99,Default,,0,0,0,,是秘密武器嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.29,0:15:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,是吧 友友
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.45,0:16:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,園子的御記有很多沒辦法讀了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.19,0:16:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我的肯定也會被塗掉很多
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.40,0:16:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,可是必須要寫
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.33,0:16:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,要努力給未來的勇者派上用場
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.70,0:16:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,咦 咦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.90,0:16:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,因為是夢嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.50,0:16:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.04,0:16:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.79,0:16:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,是我啊 你不是認識嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.48,0:16:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,高嶋？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.27,0:16:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.12,0:16:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我們長得一模一樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.85,0:16:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你是我的先祖大人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.19,0:17:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然似乎不是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.75,0:17:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,但差不多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.63,0:17:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,那個 這是夢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.28,0:17:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,果然會被這樣認為嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.05,0:17:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,說明起來太麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.60,0:17:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,就算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.05,0:17:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,不要緊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.75,0:17:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我是高嶋友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.73,0:17:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你是結城友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.03,0:17:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,太見外了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.63,0:17:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.90,0:17:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,都怪詛咒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.55,0:17:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,告訴我也不要緊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.92,0:17:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我被詛咒了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.48,0:17:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然代替東鄉很了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.31,0:17:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,但天神似乎為此發火了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.12,0:17:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,發火？ 因為這個？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.90,0:17:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我也一直在做神樹大人的一部分
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.40,0:17:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,神很隨性很難理解的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.31,0:17:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你剛才提到自己是神樹大人的一部分？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.47,0:17:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.89,0:17:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈應該也讀過了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.30,0:17:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我沒能活下來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.70,0:18:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,當時以為已經不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.17,0:18:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,但只有靈魂被神樹大人守住了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.99,0:18:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,似乎很特別
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.26,0:18:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你是靈魂嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.98,0:18:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我自己也不是很清楚 所以這樣稱呼自己
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.13,0:18:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,不是鬼魂哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.65,0:18:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,不 也算是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.67,0:18:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,不要煩惱 繼續說
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.41,0:18:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,當時友奈要是接受了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.79,0:18:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,肯定也會變成神樹大人的一部分
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.81,0:18:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,可是友奈選擇了活下去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.23,0:18:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,好厲害 了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.24,0:18:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,了不起？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.61,0:18:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我沒時間選擇
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.47,0:18:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,因為太專心了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.23,0:18:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.29,0:18:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,因為我聽到了聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.75,0:18:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,還有 大家在叫我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.63,0:18:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,真好啊 勇者部
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.07,0:18:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.61,0:18:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.09,0:18:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,關於我今天來的目的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.39,0:19:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你的詛咒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.06,0:19:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,由我來承擔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.36,0:19:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,神很可怕 很隨性
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.87,0:19:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,但也迷迷糊糊的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.57,0:19:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,迷糊？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.27,0:19:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我和友奈基本是同一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.51,0:19:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,從神的視點看來的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.72,0:19:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.03,0:19:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈已經足夠痛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.25,0:19:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我能代替你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.73,0:19:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,那友奈會怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.81,0:19:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,活在未來的你沒必要痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.44,0:19:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.82,0:19:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我真的好開心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.96,0:19:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.30,0:19:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,可是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.83,0:19:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,推給其他人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.20,0:19:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,更加痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.65,0:19:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,果然是我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.47,0:20:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.90,0:20:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,其他人痛苦最讓我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.06,0:20:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,痛苦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.10,0:20:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.23,0:20:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,今後能努力下去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.23,0:20:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,努力不下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.97,0:20:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.67,0:20:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,可是 我只能這樣做
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.83,0:20:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.50,0:20:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,能和你聊詛咒的事太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.93,0:20:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,來一趟太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.59,0:20:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,要哭嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.45,0:20:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,要哭
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.51,0:20:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,就這樣 已通知結城友奈大人現在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.85,0:20:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,作為御記留下記錄
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.41,0:20:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,把人類的生存戰略 託付給未來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.53,0:21:03.73,Default,,0,0,0,,關於這件事 元老院有新的提議
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.45,0:21:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,因為結城友奈大人的神性很高
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.11,0:21:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,所以成了御姿 才有這一情況
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.03,0:21:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,結城友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.36,0:21:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我們可能三百年
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.32,0:21:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,都在等待這樣的天才
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.53,0:21:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,以結城友奈大人的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.61,0:21:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,結束長久以來的神事的時候來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.06,0:21:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣人類就會得救
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.86,0:21:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,執行神婚之儀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.55,0:21:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,戰鬥任務？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.68,0:21:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.81,0:21:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,不是牆外調查嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.14,0:21:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,到底要我們做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.21,0:21:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,神事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.66,0:21:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,好可怕 好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.14,0:21:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,戰鬥任務… 我們防人有和神戰鬥的手段嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.83,0:22:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,先前明明沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.75,0:22:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,詳情事後通知
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.66,0:22:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,防人部隊在最終作戰中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.88,0:22:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,負責掩護正規勇者們
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.53,0:22:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,最終作戰？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.22,0:23:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝 我不會輸的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.69,0:23:50.61,Top,,0,0,0,,那個神婚是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.82,0:23:51.61,Top,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1565,27)}什麼調查
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.09,0:23:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,塔要倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.61,0:23:53.24,Top,,0,0,0,,不要做什麼勇者了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.36,0:23:52.32,Top,,0,0,0,,{\pos(322,27)}沒辦法告訴防人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.42,0:23:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,明明都不知道發生了什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.14,0:23:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我可是完成型勇者 三好夏凜！
